# The scripts directory holds inspect / dev / one-off tooling the image
# doesn't need — exclude it to keep the build context small. The exceptions are
# the bundled Cloud Run Job entrypoints: the builder stage runs `npx esbuild`
# over each to inline it into a self-contained `.cjs`, so those files (and their
# `lib/` imports) must reach the build context. Keep these negations in lockstep
# with the Dockerfile's esbuild steps.
scripts
!scripts/migrate.ts
!scripts/rebuild-indices.ts
